out of the toilet if she wanted to.

01:18.728 --> 01:21.788
Wait a minute.
Isn't she the one who dumped you?

01:21.898 --> 01:23.456
Somebody dumped Charlie?

01:23.566 --> 01:26.660
Broke his little black heart.
It was pathetic.

01:27.303 --> 01:29.134
