if she wasn't up there.

03:31.895 --> 03:34.159
Maybe she had a good reason.

03:35.798 --> 03:36.992
Maybe.

03:38.301 --> 03:40.132
Charlie, look at me.

03:45.675 --> 03:48.701
- How do you know my name?
- It's me.

03:49.679 --> 03:51.169
Me who?

03:59.589 --> 04:00.988
No.

04:03.526 --> 04:04.823
Yes.

04:06.896 --> 04:08.158
Jill?

04:08.898 --> 04:10.160
Bill.

04:14.337 --> 04:16.031
