04:27.083 --> 04:30.246
- That's okay, I don't want to...
- They're not for you.

04:30.586 --> 04:33.248
This girl you're waiting for
really must be something.

04:33.356 --> 04:36.587
Just serve the hooch
and mind your own business.

04:36.759 --> 04:39.387
- Listen, Charlie, I know...
- Hang on.

04:44.000 --> 04:45.331
