05:51.134 --> 05:54.570
- You haven't changed.
- I wish I could say the same.

05:55.304 --> 05:57.932
Charlie, how could I have explained it
to you back then?

05:58.007 --> 06:00.407
I couldn't even explain it to myself.

06:00.476 --> 06:03.172
Okay, now you've explained. Thank you.

06:04.614 --> 06:06.309
Nice to see you again.

06:06.416 --> 06:08.475
Good luck with the penis.

06:09.685 --> 06:10.982
Wait.

06:12.288 --> 06:15.849
A few minutes ago you said
I was a really cool friend.

06:16.259 --> 06:17.590
Yeah.

06:17.660 --> 06:21.687
Well, I'm back in LA and I'm kind of
starting a new life.

06:23.933 --> 06:26.925
