06:42.018 --> 06:45.476
- It's gonna be okay, Jill.
- Bill.

06:46.255 --> 06:49.622
Yeah, Bill, whatever. It's okay.

06:49.926 --> 06:51.860
I'm still your friend.

06:52.795 --> 06:55.025
Charlie, you're the best.

06:58.101 --> 07:02.003
