07:57.527 --> 08:00.553
Anyway, I ran into my old friend, Bill, here.

08:05.067 --> 08:08.230
So, stood up by Jill, ran into Bill.

08:08.771 --> 08:10.329
That's funny.

08:11.073 --> 08:13.769
