10:46.495 --> 10:48.827
All right, I'm sorry.
Why are we looking at Jill?

10:48.931 --> 10:50.922
- Just look at it.
- Okay.

10:51.500 --> 10:52.990
She's cute.

10:53.936 --> 10:55.301
